com.ethanzeigler.jgamegui.element

Class ButtonImageElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ethanzeigler.jgamegui.element.AbstractElement
      • com.ethanzeigler.jgamegui.element.ImageElement
        • com.ethanzeigler.jgamegui.element.ButtonImageElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sized, java.lang.Comparable

    public class ButtonImageElement
extends ImageElement
implements Sized
    Represents a button on the screen with a clickable area defined in the constructor and it's image.

    To strictly create a clickable area without an image attached to it, the image can be set to null and nothing will be drawn, but the clickable area will still exist.
